title: Full Auto Conversion Guide Collection- Update #2
description:
This is simply an update of my previous torrent...it has all the same content, with newer things on top of it.  To show how much new stuff has been added, the previous torrent was about 40MB...  In the future this will be updated as well, this is just what I have organized so far.

The firearms discussed:

AK-47, AR-15/M-16, AR-7, Cobray M-11-9 Pistol, Colt M1911/M1911A1, Glock 17/18, HK-91, HK-94, Uzi, Mac-10, Marlin .22, Ruger 10-22, Ruger Mini-14, SKS, Tec-9 and KG-99.  While the list remains about the same from the previous torrent, the amount of literature on the firearms has roughly doubled.

Furthermore, there are numerous articles on general full-auto conversion, and the tools and techniques used to do so.
